      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone willing to invest a bit of effort into its upkeep. The engine starts and runs consistently, though it shows signs of age and would benefit from a comprehensive tune-up and fluid flush. The transmission shifts through all gears, but the engagement is not as crisp as it once was. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading paint on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few small tears, though the dashboard and electronics remain largely functional. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that provides a great foundation for gradual improvement.",
