      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the high-revving S65 V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a linear power delivery that peaks at its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is outfitted with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for precise gear engagement and lightning-fast shift points. Recent mechanical upkeep includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the long-term integrity of the valvetrain. With its M-tuned suspension and variable differential lock, this vehicle offers exceptional turn-in response and maintains its factory-spec structural rigidity for a visceral driving experience.",
