    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S is a meticulously maintained example of performance meeting utility. Finished in a sophisticated Volcano Grey Metallic, the exterior retains a deep, glossy luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia typical of highway driving, the body is straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a testament to German engineering. The premium black leather upholstery remains supple and clean, with no tears or unpleasant odors, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every feature, including the panoramic glass sunroof, heated seats, and the crisp Bose surround sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this Macan is in its prime. It boasts a comprehensive service history with all scheduled maintenance performed on time. The twin-turbo V6 engine pulls strongly and smoothly, paired with a PDK transmission that shifts with surgical precision. With recent brake service and tires that offer plenty of tread, this vehicle is ready for the road with no immediate work required. It is a complete package for the discerning driver who wants Porsche performance in a dependable, well-cared-for package.",
